# Cargo / Rust
/target/
**/*.rs.bk
Cargo.lock.bak

# Editors
.idea/
.vscode/
*.swp
*.swo
.DS_Store

# Local secrets / runtime state — do NOT commit
.env
.env.*
!.env.example
*.pem
*.key

# Operator-local WORKFLOW.md (the example file is committed; the live one is per-machine).
# `docker/WORKFLOW.md` is the operator's customized copy of `docker/WORKFLOW.example.md`
# that gets bind-mounted into the sinfonia daemon container; it holds project-specific
# values (Linear slug, repo slug) and should not be tracked.
/WORKFLOW.md
/docker/WORKFLOW.md

# Workspace dirs (if someone runs from inside the repo)
/symphony-workspaces/
/sinfonia-workspaces/

# Coverage / profiling
/coverage/
*.profraw
*.profdata
